<p>[COMMENT by Lorenzo: I've been tempted from time to time to describe some of the DMT visuals in my own words, rather than Terence's, but if I do then I'll be doing the same thing he did by limiting one's own thoughts about these things. My advice is to forget everything that anyone has said about what they look like and just go with your own vision. After all, what, exactly, is a "jeweled self-dribbling basketball"? All I can do is to add another layer of confusion on a visual experience that I suspect is quite similar for all of us but one which we all use different words to describe. . . . that's why some of these experiences are classified as "ineffable" I guess :-).]</p>
		
